sequenceDiagram
    participant User
    participant React as React Frontend
    participant Fast as FastAPI Router
    participant Sup as Supervisor (LLM)
    participant Loc as Locality Agent
    participant Map as Heatmap Plotter
    participant MCP as MCP Server (Mindat)

    User->>React: "Map minerals in Korea"
    React->>Fast: POST /api/agent/chat
    Fast->>Sup: Start Graph Workflow

    Note over Sup: Reasoning: Need location data
    Sup->>Loc: Route to Locality Collector
    Loc->>MCP: collect_localities(country="Korea")
    MCP-->>Loc: Locality data
    Loc-->>Sup: Data ready

    Note over Sup: Reasoning: Generate visualization
    Sup->>Map: Route to Heatmap Plotter
    Map->>MCP: heatmap_plot(data)
    MCP-->>Map: map.html
    Map-->>Sup: Map ready

    Sup->>Fast: FINISH
    Fast-->>React: Response + plot_url
    React-->>User: Display map